Surf_ny_exploder_prime
by FAJ
--------------------------------------------
Combat surf map, much like the original master_exploder, to which this is a sequel to. Trying to bring back the combat map over the monotonous skill-surf. I hope you enjoy it.

Bombsite enables at bottom of map after a minute and thirty seconds. Included mostly to truncate long rounds times. Most weapons are include in the map, but more importantly, there are enough shotguns for everyone :).

designed for 66 tick, 150 airaccelerate

Comments/critisicm are welcome, as always.
